quran[8{c,v,t}:
34,15,"Saba ke liye unn ke apne maskan hi mein aik nishani mojood thi, do baagh dayen aur baen khao apne rab ka diya howa rizaq aur shukar baja lao uss ka, malik hai umdah o pakeeza aur parvar-digaar hai bakhshish frmane wala"
34,16,magar woh mun mourr gay aakhir kaar hum ne unn par band toar selaab bhaij diya aur un ke pichlle do baghoon ki jagah do aur baagh inhen diye jin mein karvae kaseelay phal aur jhar ke darakht thay aur kuch thori si beriyaan
34,17,"yeh tha un ke kufar ka badla jo hum ne un ko diya, aur nashukray ensaan ke siwa aisa badla hum aur kisi ko nahi dete"
34,18,"aur hum ne unn ke aur unn bustiyon ke darmain, jin ko hum ne barket ataa ki thi, numaya bastiyan basa di theen aur unn mein safar ki musaftain aik andazay par rakh di theen chalo phiro inn raastoon mein raat din poooray aman ke sath"
34,19,"magar unhon ne kaha"" ae hamaray rab, hamaray safar ki musaftain lambi kar day"" unhon ne apne oopar aap zulm kya aakhir kaar hum ne inhen afsana bana kar rakh diya aur inhen bilkul tittar bittar kar dala yaqeenan is mein nishanain hain har uss shakhs ke liye jo bara sabir o Shakir ho"
34,20,"unn ke maamla mein iblees ne apna gumaan sahih paaya aur unhon ne usi ki pairwi ki, bajuz aik thoray se giroh ke jo momin tha"
34,21,iblees ko unn par koi Iqtidaar haasil nah tha magar jo kuch howa woh is liye howa ke hum yeh dekhna chahtay thay ke kon akhirat ka maan-ne wala hai aur kon is ki taraf se shak mein para howa hai tera rab har cheez par nigran hai
34,22,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn mushriqeen se ) kaho ke pukaar dekho apne unn mabodon ko jinhein tum Allah ke siwa apna mabood samjhay baithy ho woh nah asmano mein kisi zarra barabar cheez ke maalik hain nah zameen mein woh aasman o zameen ki malkiat mein shareek bhi nahi hain un mein se koi Allah ka madad gaar bhi nahi hai"
